      public String paymentType
      Payment type. 'External' is returned for forwarded numbers which are not terminated in the RingCentral phone system Enum: External, TollFree, Local, BusinessMobileNumberProvider, ExternalNumberProvider

    • phoneNumber

      public String phoneNumber
      Phone number

    • primary

      public Boolean primary
      Indicates if a phone number is primary, i.e. displayed as 'main number' and called by default

    • status

      public String status
      Status of a phone number. If the value is 'Normal', the phone number is ready to be used. Otherwise, it is an external number not yet ported to RingCentral Enum: Normal, Pending, PortedIn, Temporary

    • type

      public String type
      Phone number type Enum: VoiceFax, FaxOnly, VoiceOnly

    • subType

      public String subType
      Extension subtype, if applicable. For any unsupported subtypes the 'Unknown' value will be returned Enum: VideoPro, VideoProPlus, DigitalSignage, Unknown

    • usageType

      public String usageType
      Usage type of phone number. Numbers of 'NumberPool' type will not be returned for phone number list requests Enum: MainCompanyNumber, AdditionalCompanyNumber, CompanyNumber, DirectNumber, CompanyFaxNumber, ForwardedNumber, ForwardedCompanyNumber, ContactCenterNumber, ConferencingNumber, NumberPool, BusinessMobileNumber, PartnerBusinessMobileNumber, IntegrationNumber

    • features

      public String[] features
      List of features of a phone number Enum: CallerId, SmsSender, A2PSmsSender, MmsSender, InternationalSmsSender, Delegated
